{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tadeht preezajahs manna Sir̄s/ un mans Gohds lihg̅-mojahs/ ir manna Meeta dsh-wohs drehtchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tu ne pamettifi man-ni Kappā/ tu ne liksi tawam Swehtam to Satruhdeschanu redseht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu darri man tahs Dsh-wibas Zettu sinnama/ preeksch tawa Waiga irr Lihgfinotchanu Pilniba/ un mihliga Buhshana pee tawas labbas Rohkas muh-schigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta XVII. Dseefma.\nIrr weena luhdsama Dseefma/ ka Deews fa-wu kristitu Draudsibu pee weseligas Mah-zibas un swehtas Dshwochanas gribbetu usturreht: 5/ 6. Prett teem wiltigeem Mahzitajeem un mihfsteem Swehteem/ kas ar Zilweku Mahzibahm un Darbeem no Dee-wa Wahrda nowadda: 4.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Eena Luhgschana Dah-wida: KUNGS pa-flaust to Taifnibu/ nem wehrā mannu Brehfschanu/grees tawas Anjis us mannu Luhgschanu/ kas no wiltigahm Luhpahm ne nahk.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Lai manna Teefa no te-wim spreesfa tohp/ tawas Azjis stattahs us to/ kas Taifniba irr-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu pahrmanni mannu Sir̄di/ to peemekle to Naktis/tu effi manni kausejs un neeka-ne atraddis es esinu apschmees/ka manna Muttei ne buhs pahr-tahpt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es pafargohs eekſch tawu Luhpu Wahrdn/ preeksch Zilwe-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "ku Darbeem/ us ta Laupitaja Pehdahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ustuiri mannis Gabju-mus ustaweem Zelteem/ ka man-ni Sohti ne schaubahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es tewis peefanzu/ tu gribbi mannis paklausyht ak Deews! greestawu Aufi pee man-nim/ klausi mannu Wallodu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Parahdi brihnigi tawu Scheblastibu/ tu Pestitajs to/kas us tewi palaischahs/ prett teem/ kas prett tawu labbu Roh-ku Zettahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pafargi mannis ka weenu Azzrangii Azzi/ aptlep manni appakſch tawu Spahrnu Ehnas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Preeksch to Besdeewigii Waiga/ kas manni pohsti/preeksch mannas Dwehteles Eenaidnee-feem/ kas apkahrt manni met-tahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee irr tauki isbarroju-fchees/ ar fatwu Mutti runna tee leptii.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee mettahs muhfds Gabjumds apkahrt mumis/ ar jawahm Azzin tee gluhsna muhs pee Semnes peegahst.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wixnu Eihnis irr ka weena Lauwa/ kam lauptibt gri-bahs/ un ka weens janis Lau-wa/ kas Sleppeniba fehsch.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Zettees KUNGS/ stet-dsees winnam pretti/ noleez win-xu/ isglabb manni Dwehselt ar tawu Sohbinu no ta Besdee-wiga.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No teem* Laudun ta-was Rohkas ak KUNGS! no teem\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
